## Project Structure

```
expense_audit_env/
├── openenv.yaml          # OpenEnv manifest
├── pyproject.toml         # Package configuration
├── models.py              # Pydantic models (Action, Observation, etc.)
├── client.py              # EnvClient subclass
├── __init__.py            # Package exports
├── inference.py           # Baseline inference script
├── Dockerfile             # Container image
├── README.md              # This file
└── server/
    ├── app.py             # FastAPI application
    ├── audit_environment.py  # Core environment logic
    ├── scenarios.py       # Deterministic scenario generator
    ├── graders.py         # Scoring and grading logic
    ├── requirements.txt   # Server dependencies
    └── Dockerfile         # Server Dockerfile (alt)
```

